creator: Solo Tech Apps
descriptionHtml:
With this speed tracker app you can find any vehicle or travel speed like walking, jogging, biking, driving speed. Speedometer odometer HUDView is one of the best app to find any vehicle speed if you have broken Car, or Motorcycle speedometer.

Car speedometer offline app has simple and attractive user interface

Speed tracker App Has Following Features
App Usage
Speed tracker app is all in one app and can be use it for different purpose like speedometer for bike, speedometer for car, speedometer for bicycle, speedometer for train, speedometer for running or train speed checker
Even you can find aeroplane and ships speed with there live location using map
You can use this app as a ski tracker to record your tracking history while skiing

Different Speed Units
Find your any vehicles speed in MPH, KMPH, and KNOT

Multiple Speed View Options
Speed can be view in different speedometer views like current speed with detail options screen, full screen current speed only which is very helpful while driving
HUD Mod / HUD View in which you can see your the car speed and other information by reflecting view on your car’s windscreen
Map View allow you to track and view your current speed or other details in live map

App is design for both screen orientation like landscape and portrait view so choose those which is best for you.
Detail Information and Tracking History.
You can see detailed information about your trip which is Current Speed, Maximum Speed, Average Speed, Trip Distance etc.

Record and save all the trip information inside app and can view it later any time
Also can view speed information speed chart or in graphical representation

Speedometer Offline
Speedometer online app require only internet connection when you use map view functionality otherwise all other app features works perfectly without internet connection

Please contact us at solotechapps@gmail.com if you have any question or suggestion regarding this app.
